annotationA: Ribosomal protein L22-like is a eukaryotic-specific component of the large ribosomal subunit involved in protein synthesis
annotationB: 40S ribosomal protein S4; Structural constituent of ribosome; RNA binding. It is involved in the biological process described with: mitotic spindle elongation; centrosome organization; translation; centrosome duplication; mitotic spindle organization; Belongs to the eukaryotic ribosomal protein eS4 family
